  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Purpose: to compare Laparoscopic mesh rectopexy with laparoscopic suture rectopexy Patient
      and Methods: The prospective study was conducted at Pediatric Surgery Department, Al-Azhar
      university hospitals, Cairo, Egypt . The operative time, recurrence rate, post-operative
      constipation, and effect on fecal incontinence, were reported and evaluated for each group
    </textblock>
